OL,3,CSome employers 'cautious of offering
OL,4,Cfinancial advice due to reputation
OL,5,Cworries'
OL,7,FSome employers are being put off from
OL,8,Foffering financial advice as a
OL,9,Fworkplace benefit amid concerns that
OL,10,Fit could potentially end up reflecting
OL,11,Fbadly on them, a survey has found.
OL,13,FA third (34%) of organisations do not
OL,14,Foffer financial advice, rising to just
OL,15,Fover half (51%) of organisations with
OL,16,Ffewer than 500 employees, the research
OL,17,Findicated.
